race.comment: AREYA TUCHUZY (2) was far from disgraced when third last start over 1200m at Morven, beaten a head. That followed a win at this track the start prior. Has a good record at this course and distance, including three wins and has strong winning prospects. ACEDROD (1) scored at his most recent appearance, getting home by 2 lengths over 1400m at Mitchell as favourite. That continued the very strong form this campaign, with three wins from five outings. Rates among the leading players again. BORN FEARLESS (6) turned in a decent effort last start to finish third over 1200m at Chinchilla. Likely improver so plenty to like about his chances. PALATIAL PRINCE (4) is racing well and is not to be discounted.
